OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FEngland play Mexico at 1am on Monday 6
OL,7,FJuly in their next World Cup knockout
OL,8,Fmatch.
OL,10,FMexicans living in Ambleside in the
OL,11,FLake District are getting into the
OL,12,Fspirit, enjoying the fun with their
OL,13,FEnglish friends and customers:
OL,15,FWhile some Cumbrian fans have said
OL,16,Fthey will watch the game on catch up,
OL,17,Fmany are planning to stay up to see
OL,18,Fthe drama as it unfolds, as pubs have
OL,19,Fbeen given special licenses to stay
OL,20,Fopen until 5am.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FEnglish fans in West Cumbria told ITV
OL,7,FBorder why they're hoping for a win,
OL,8,F"It's coming home" said one as he
OL,9,Fpredicted the score would be 3-1 to
OL,10,FEngland, while another thinks it will
OL,11,Fbe much closer at 2-1 after extra time.
OL,13,FThe Landlord of the Lion and the Lamb
OL,14,Fin Gosforth, Richard Mawson, has his
OL,15,Fprediction too: "I think we're too
OL,16,Fwobbly at the back, so I think Mexico
OL,17,Fwill score."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FHe continued, "But as long as we're
OL,7,Fdoing, like the vindaloo song, and we
OL,8,Fscore one more than them, we'll beat
OL,9,Fthem. And we have the world class
OL,10,Fstrikers Harry Kane, Jude Bellingham,
OL,11,FDeclan Rice, Saka the best in the
OL,12,Fworld, the best in the business.
OL,13,FThere's absolutely no reason we can't
OL,14,Fscore one more goal than them."
OL,16,FBut Mexicans living in Ambleside have
OL,17,Fanother story.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FMexican restaurant Tacos del Sol is
OL,7,Frun by a Mexican woman and British
OL,8,Fman, with their son of both
OL,9,Fallegiances.
OL,11,FHead chef Sebastian Velazquillo Kidd
OL,12,Ftold us who to support is a tough
OL,13,Fquestion, "I'm half British and half
OL,14,FMexican. If I was in a pub, I think
OL,15,FI'd support England, but if I was
OL,16,Fsurrounded by all my Mexican friends,
OL,17,FI think I would have to say Mexico",
OL,18,Fadding with a nervous look at his
OL,19,Fmother, "and my Mom as well."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FMexican Ivana Rico works at the
OL,7,Frestaurant while studying at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Cumbria's Ambleside
OL,9,Fcampus and told ITV Border, "I came
OL,10,Fhere last September for my ecology
OL,11,Fcourse here in Ambleside. Obviously I
OL,12,Fsupport Mexico till the end and I feel
OL,13,Flike Mexico is going to win."
OL,15,FIvana's family and friends are
OL,16,Fcurrently visiting from Mexico so will
OL,17,Fbe watching the game while here in the
OL,18,FUK.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
