PN,32806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FDaniel Alanis says he is really
OL,7,Fenjoying sharing football with English
OL,8,Ffans, "I'm from Mexico City. I
OL,9,Factually live a little bit nearby to
OL,10,Fthe stadium where the game is going to
OL,11,Fhappen. The passion British people
OL,12,Fhave for football to the Mexican one,
OL,13,Fit's really similar. We really support
OL,14,Four teams. We love them. We feel them.
OL,15,FThere is so much emotions."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FThey all believe Mexico will win
OL,7,Fbecause they have been on better form
OL,8,Fthis year. Ana Bermechea explains,
OL,9,F"This time Mexicans are saying 'Es i
OL,10,Fsi', which means 'what if?' What if
OL,11,Fthis time we win? So 'Es i si'. I
OL,12,Fbelieve we win", she says before
OL,13,Fhollering with gusto, "We Are Mexico!"
OL,15,FThey will be visiting Edinburgh when
OL,16,Fthe match is on, so they are hoping to
OL,17,Ffind some Scottish support for their
OL,18,Fteam.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783698492
OL,3,CEnglish and Mexican fans in Cumbria
OL,4,Cgear up for World Cup match
OL,6,FLuis Fernandez made his pitch to the
OL,7,FScots, "I really know the relationship
OL,8,Fbetween Scotland and England so any
OL,9,FScottish fans can support us."
OL,11,FDaniel Alanis adds, "We have a phrase
OL,12,Fthat we say to the one that's for
OL,13,FMexico, that is, 'Hermano el es
OL,14,FMexicano' that in English is ,
OL,15,F'brother, you are now Mexican'."
OL,17,FThat is their message for those north
OL,18,Fof the border, as fans on both sides
OL,19,Fgear up for the match that decides
OL,20,Ftheir future in this football World
OL,21,FCup.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
